{"tid":672968,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"好樂隊推介：Without You原唱者 Badfinger","createTime":"2018-05-21T12:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T17:24:34.000Z","uid":40662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65135f4f0bc674d872bade88c999e43987b70b72","tid":672968,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/201442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F201442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f2c8ca94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBadfinger，一隊曾經被外界稱為「窮人版Beatles」嘅苦命組合，五年前，當大熱美劇【Breaking Bad】全五季播放完畢，一首既熟悉又陌生嘅英文老歌就喺主角Walter White臨終前一刻徐徐響起，呢首聽起嚟相當有feel嘅片尾曲喺當時除咗引起一眾影迷熱烈討論之外，佢嘅點擊率亦隨住套劇嘅熱度而大幅上升，呢首hit爆全城嘅片尾曲叫做〈Baby Blue〉，係收錄喺Badfinger一張名叫《Straight Up》嘅專輯入面，或者有好多朋友都係透過呢首歌先認識到Badfinger呢個名字，但以我嚟講，其實早喺十幾年前我就已經比呢支樂隊嘅其中一首經典作品〈Carry On Till Tomorrow〉深深吸引，仲因為咁而專登走去唱片舖買咗佢哋嘅一張精選碟返屋企。噚晚，我心血來潮寫咗一篇長文，希望可以令到更多人認識到呢隊樂隊，喺呢篇文章入面我除咗會細數一下呢隊band嘅歷史之外，仲會嚴選自己最喜愛嘅Badfinger歌曲Top 50。🖖<br />\n<br />\n完整全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2018/05/Badfinger.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2018%2F05%2FBadfinger.html&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=dabe8142\" target=\"_blank\">https://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2018/05/Badfinger.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/201456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F201456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=454d007c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71060fe41b685933c380399f7d856aa20efbad82","tid":672968,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{